outputs.output_descr: Building of national institutions to plan for, monitor and evaluate the use of national resources is primary objective for the project, through sectors. Support will also be provided to increase management of aid effectiveness and sharing of information for all development partners. The generation of timely and needed information will also be supported for the central statistic office. All the undertaking will be guided by the national global MDG objectives.

project_title: Strengthening National Capacities for Poverty Reduction
